name: Dragon Immortal of Tenyi
desc:
2 Wyrm monsters
You can discard 1 card, then target 1 Wyrm monster in your GY; Special Summon it, also you cannot activate the effects of monsters that were Special Summoned from the Extra Deck for the rest of this turn, except "Tenyi" monsters. When an attack is declared involving your face-up non-Effect Monster: You can target 1 card your opponent controls; destroy it. You can only use each effect of "Dragon Immortal of Tenyi" once per turn.
